        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "These grouses molt through the seasons, appearing all white in the spring and shifting to a mix of brown and white in winter months.<br/><br/> Ptarmigans are roughly a foot long from beak to tail and have a wingspan of twice that."
